with-summary field-label-hidden\">\r\n<div class=\"field-items\">\r\n<div class=\"field-item even\">\r\n\r\nOn a recent trip to Denmark for Copenhagen Fashion Week, it was clear the real fashion shows weren’t inside the venues, they were on the streets.\r\n\r\nMost attendees were industry members, dressed to the nines entering shows late in the hope that street style photographers would snap them.\r\n\r\nIf you ask any Danish person how they would describe Copenhagen street style, they can sum it up in a couple of words: relaxed, mish-mashed and trend-oriented.\r\n\r\nMost of the focus that week was on women, so I decided to document what the men wore.\r\n\r\nIt was evident there was a strong industrial/East Berlin/techno/Goscha vibe influencing the men of Copenhagen.\r\n\r\nSportswear was the strongest element to trend, true to Scandinavia’s relaxed approach to fashion. Sneakers were the main choice of footwear, paired with combinations lying somewhere between dressy and casual. These men were a far cry from the army of suits at Pitti Uomo.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/carlosmangubat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">instagram.com/carlosmangubat</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"panel-pane pane-entity-field pane-node-field-photography-name\">\r\n<div class=\"field field-name-field-photography-name field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"field-label\">Photography:</div>\r\n<div class=\"field-items\">\r\n<div class=\"field-item even\">Carlos Mangubat</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Street snaps: Men\'s style in Copenhagen','','inherit','closed','closed','','716-revision-v1','','','2017-09-25 08:03:28','2017-09-25 08:03:28','',716,'http://localhost/uncategorized/716-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(773,4,'2017-09-25 08:09:01','2017-09-25 08:09:01','Rihanna’s <a href=\"http://www.fashionjournal.com.au/fashion/news/rihannas-fenty-puma-aw17-collection-gets-release-date\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fenty Puma AW17 collection</a> is set to drop in just eight days and there are a few products which we’ve already got our eyes on. Namely the Fenty Mascot backpack.\r\n\r\nShaped like a giant teddy bear, the bag has adjustable straps, top carrying handle and zipper down the back.\r\n\r\nThe teddy features black pompom ears, button eyes and a giant varsity-inspired F on its belly. From what we\'ve seen, it\'ll be available in a few colourways.\r\n\r\nIt seems a select few of these unbearably cute bags have already been and gone at Urban Outfitters, so you’ll have to wait until September 28 before you can get your hands on one. If you\'re really keen to get ahead of the crowd, a selection of other Fenty accessories from the collection is available from the retailer now, including <a href=\"https://www.urbanoutfitters.com/shop/puma-fenty-by-rihanna-hike-backpack?category=SHOPBYBRAND&amp;color=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this </a>hiking bag.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://au.puma.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">au.puma.com</a>','The next Fenty Puma release includes a teddy bear backpack','','publish','open','open','','the-next-fenty-puma-release-includes-a-teddy-bear-backpack','','','2017-09-25 08:09:01','2017-09-25 08:09:01','',0,'http://localhost/?p=773',0,'post','',0),(774,4,'2017-09-25 08:08:13','2017-09-25 08:08:13','','fenty-rihanna-teddy-backpack-01','','inherit','open','closed','','fenty-rihanna-teddy-backpack-01','','','2017-09-25 08:08:13','2017-09-25 08:08:13','',773,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/fenty-rihanna-teddy-backpack-01.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(775,4,'2017-09-25 08:08:15','2017-09-25 08:08:15','','fenty-rihanna-teddy-backpack-02','','inherit','open','closed','','fenty-rihanna-teddy-backpack-02','','','2017-09-25 08:08:15','2017-09-25 08:08:15','',773,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/fenty-rihanna-teddy-backpack-02.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(776,4,'2017-09-25 08:08:17','2017-0