608.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(886,4,'2017-09-25 09:14:03','2017-09-25 09:14:03','','5TH_08 25 2017 â-- LTD Pt2_615','','inherit','open','closed','','5th_08-25-2017-a-ltd-pt2_615','','','2017-09-25 09:14:03','2017-09-25 09:14:03','',879,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/5TH_08-25-2017-â-LTD-Pt2_615.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(887,4,'2017-09-25 09:15:16','2017-09-25 09:15:16','Australian lifestyle brand, The 5TH, has just expanded its accessories range with the addition of a new tote.\r\n\r\nDubbed The Everyday Tote, the bag is unisex and designed to be tote-ally convenient (sorry had to).\r\n\r\nThe brand has shown a real understanding of the modern customer\'s needs with this release. The tote comes in two colourways - a micro suede grey and waxed canvas black. All detailing is in a plush black leather and the interior is made from neoprene.\r\n\r\nIt also features individual compartments for those of you who hold up queues at the supermarket while rummaging for your wallet (you know who you are).\r\n\r\nThe Everyday Tote Bag is available now.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.the5th.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the5th.co</a>','The 5TH just added a tote bag to its accessories lineup','','inherit','closed','closed','','879-revision-v1','','','2017-09-25 09:15:16','2017-09-25 09:15:16','',879,'http://localhost/uncategorized/879-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(888,4,'2017-09-25 09:21:46','2017-09-25 09:21:46','Being fairly isolated here in the Southern Hemisphere, we can feel so far away from the action up north. Especially when we miss out on the best sneakers because they never make it across the seas.\r\n\r\nBut fret no longer. We’ve done some research to find you eight of the coolest newly-released sneakers available Down Under.\r\n\r\n<strong>Vans Fuzzy Suede 23</strong>\r\n\r\nVelcro is back and we can’t get enough. Not only is this shoe convenient, it’s also incredibly plush with its fuzzy suede upper in powder blue.\r\n\r\n<strong>Price: </strong>$129.95\r\n<strong>Buy it </strong><strong>at:</strong><strong> </strong><a href=\"https://www.platypusshoes.com.au/fuzzy-suede-style-23-v-1.html#93=8495\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Platypus</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Superga 2790 Pusnakew Platform Sneaker</strong>\r\n\r\nIconic Italian footwear label Superga recently sent some new releases our way and it feels good to be included. The 2790 is a classic tennis shoe and has added height with a platform sole. The addition of a snakeskin upper makes for some real ‘90s vibes.\r\n\r\n<strong>Price: </strong>$119.95\r\n<strong>But it </strong><strong>at:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.gluestore.com.au/superga-womens-2790-pusnakew-platform-sneakers-in-beige-khaki-silver.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Glue Store</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Reebok Club C 85 Zip</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Club C 85 range has received a lot of attention and not just because Gigi Hadid modelled in the campaign. This no-muss no-fuss shoe subs out laces in exchange for an industrial metal zip, giving it a streamlined look. Plus it comes in a fresh millennial pink, which is always a good thing.\r\n\r\n<strong>Price:</strong> $149.95\r\n<strong>Buy it </strong><strong>at:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.culturekings.com.au/collections/womens-footwear/products/reebok-reebok-women-s-club-c-85-zip-pink-white\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Culture Kings </a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Converse Jack Purcell</strong>\r\n\r\nOn a more monochromatic note, Converse’s stark white Jack Purcell is an excellent everyday companion. It comes with a perforated leather upper and has that signature ‘Jack Purcell’ smile across its toe.\r\n\r\n<strong>Price:</strong> $180\r\n<strong>Buy it </strong><strong>at:</strong><a href=\"https://www.converse.com.au/jack-purcell-modern-perf-leather-low-top-white-white-white-white-157815\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Converse </a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Nike Zoom Spiridon SI </strong>\r\n\r\nFor some pumped up kicks that you can take to the track, this Nike release is a good choice. The Zoom Spiridon is lightweight, breathable and accented with some dreamy pastel detailing.\r\n\r\n<strong>Price:</strong> $229.95\r\n<strong>Buy it </strong><strong>at:</strong><strong> </strong><a href=\"https://www.solefiness.com/collections/new-arrivals/products/nike-zoom-spiridon-si-black-plum-fog-igloo-881182-003\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Solefiness </a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Puma Basket Heart</strong>\r\n\r\nIt’s no secret we love Puma’s Basket Heart. The Basket sneaker is one of the most iconic silhouettes around, it even made it into the Trainer Hall of Fame (yeah that’s a thing). We’ve fallen hard for the new Natural Vachetta colourway, which features a smooth leather upper, a suede toe and satin laces.\r\n\r\n<strong>Price:</strong> $150\r\n<strong>Buy it </strong><strong>at:</strong><a href=\"https://www.jd-sports.com.au/product/brown-puma-basket-heart-premium-womens/1016848_jdsportsau/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> JD Sports</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>adidas Stan Smith</strong>\r\n\r\nYet again adidas has elevated the Stan Smith. This time around, the sneaker gets a dual-layered leather upper finished off with geometric laser-cut detailing.\r\n\r\n<strong>Price:</strong> $150\r\n<strong>Buy it </strong><strong>at:</strong><strong> </strong><a href=\"https://www.platypusshoes.com.au/womens-stan-smith.html#93=6796\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Platypus </a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Golden Goose Super Stars</strong>\r\n\r\nThese sneakers come pre-scuffed, so you don’t have to look like you’re wearing anything too ‘new’. They also has grey suede detailing, which goes excellently with the distressed leather and smudged rubber soles.\r\n\r\n<strong>Price: </strong>$520\r\n<strong>Buy it </strong><strong>at:</strong><strong> </strong><a href=\"https://www.sneakerboy.com/shop-sneakers/golden-goose-wmns-superstar-sneakers-fw17ggdb14.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sneakerboy</a>','8 new sneaker releases that you can actually get in Aus','','publish','open','open','','8-new-sneaker-releases-that-you-can-actually-get-in-aus','','','2017-09-25 09:21:46','2017-09-25 09:21:46','',0,'http://localhost/?p=888',0,'post','',0),(889,4,'2017-09-25 09:20:11','2017-09-25 09:20:11','','65-Golden-Goose-Women-s-White-Silver-Superstar-Low-Top-Sneakers-1_1','','inherit','open','closed','','65-golden-goose-women-s-white-silver-superstar-low-top-sneakers-1_1','','','2017-09-25 09:20:11','2017-09-25 09:20:11','',888,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/65-Golden-Goose-Women-s-White-Silver-Superstar-Low-Top-Sneakers-1_1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(890,4,'2017-09-25 09:20:12','2017-09-25 09:20:12','','157815_white_1_1','','inherit','open','closed','','157815_white_1_1','','','2017-09-25 09:20:12','2017-09-25 09:20:12','',888,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/157815_white_1_1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(891,4,'2017-09-25 09:20:14','2017-09-25 09:20:14','','4058031391532_normal_0001_1024x1024_1','','inherit','open','closed','','4058031391532_normal_0001_1024x1024_1','','','2017-09-25 09:20:14','2017-09-25 09:20:14','',888,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/4058031391532_normal_0001_1024x1024_1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(892,4,'2017-09-25 09:20:15','2017-09-25 09:20:15','','bz0393.wht_bz0393_wht_01_58086_1','','inherit','open','closed','','bz0393-wht_bz0393_wht_01_58086_1','','','2017-09-25 09:20:15','2017-09-25 09:20:15','',888,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bz0393.wht_bz0393_wht_01_58086_1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(893,4,'2017-09-25 09:20:17','2017-09-25 09:20:17','','nike-zoom-spiridon-si-881182-003-womens-sneaker-black-plum-fog-igloo-01_1','','inherit','open','closed','','nike-zoom-spiridon-si-881182-003-womens-sneaker-black-plum-fog-igloo-01_1','','','2017-09-25 09:20:17','2017-09-25 09:20:17','',888,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/nike-zoom-spiridon-si-881182-003-womens-