-09-25 10:30:21','2017-09-25 10:30:21','Whether it’s cutting off, sewing on or dyeing denim, wearers of Levi’s jeans have customised their jeans for decades.\r\n\r\nThe latest drop from the brand has been inspired by this creativity, but this time Levi\'s has done all the customisation for you.\r\n\r\n<em>Altered </em>takes some of the label’s most notable styles and deconstructs and alters them to create one-of-a-kind pieces.\r\n\r\nThe women’s Trucker jacket, for example, has been given a leaner silhouette by shifting seams. The men’s version has also received a vintage worn-in look by removing pieces from the garment after washing.\r\n\r\nYou’ll also notice the classic sewed-on patch – found on the back of most Levi’s jeans – has been removed, creating a shadow effect on the back.\r\n\r\nThe <em>Altered </em>collection has just launched online, check it out <a href=\"http://www.levis.com.au/catalogsearch/result/?q=altered\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.levis.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">levis.com.au</a>','Levi’s has customised its new denim collection for you','','publish','open','open','','levis-has-customised-its-new-denim-collection-for-you','','','2017-09-25 10:30:21','2017-09-25 10:30:21','',0,'http://localhost/?p=966',0,'post','',0),(967,4,'2017-09-25 10:29:21','2017-09-25 10:29:21','','72dpi-240616a25a-17_H2_ALTERED_W8_M9_3163_RGB-3300x5100','','inherit','open','closed','','72dpi-240616a25a-17_h2_altered_w8_m9_3163_rgb-3300x5100','','','2017-09-25 10:29:21','2017-09-25 10:29:21','',966,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/72dpi-240616a25a-17_H2_ALTERED_W8_M9_3163_RGB-3300x5100.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(968,4,'2017-09-25 10:29:23','2017-09-25 10:29:23','','72dpi-2406016d89-17_H2_ALTERED_M_9_3092_RGB-3300x5100','','inherit','open','closed','','72dpi-2406016d89-17_h2_altered_m_9_3092_rgb-3300x5100','','','2017-09-25 10:29:23','2017-09-25 10:29:23','',966,'http://localhost/wp-conten