yles and deconstructs and alters them to create one-of-a-kind pieces.\r\n\r\nThe women’s Trucker jacket, for example, has been given a leaner silhouette by shifting seams. The men’s version has also received a vintage worn-in look by removing pieces from the garment after washing.\r\n\r\nYou’ll also notice the classic sewed-on patch – found on the back of most Levi’s jeans – has been removed, creating a shadow effect on the back.\r\n\r\nThe <em>Altered </em>collection has just launched online, check it out <a href=\"http://www.levis.com.au/catalogsearch/result/?q=altered\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.levis.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">levis.com.au</a>','Levi’s has customised its new denim collection for you','','inherit','closed','closed','','966-revision-v1','','','2017-09-25 10:30:21','2017-09-25 10:30:21','',966,'http://localhost/uncategorized/966-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(979,4,'2017-09-25 10:33:21','2017-09-25 10:33:21','Petflair is the only real way to bond with your animal friend in 2017.\r\n\r\nJoining the ranks of novelties like <a href=\"http://fashionjournal.com.au/fashion/news/theres-friendship-necklace-you-can-share-your-dog-because-love\">dog friendship necklaces</a> and <a href=\"http://fashionjournal.com.au/lifestyle/news/you-can-now-buy-dog-and-cat-vino-ensure-you-never-drink-alone-again\">cat wine</a>, you can now get your pet custom-printed on swimwear.\r\n\r\nThe idea began with a Kickstarter campaign, which has already raised just over $8000 for the cause in one day. It still has 27 days to go.\r\n\r\nPledgers can choose between a range of one-pieces, bikinis, towels and men’s briefs, and upload their own custom photo of their doggo or beloved pet.\r\n\r\nThe example designs are as cute as they are terrifying, but it’s all for a good cause. 25% of the proceeds will go towards Pound Paws, a charity that finds loving owners for animals on death row.\r\n\r\nSo if you’re interested