ion-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1000,4,'2017-09-26 02:45:28','2017-09-26 02:45:28','It\'s been just over a day since Moschino\'s <em>My Little Pony</em>collection <a href=\"http://fashionjournal.com.au//fashion/news/moschino-just-launched-my-little-pony-collection-milan-fashion-week\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">debuted</a> at Milan Fashion Week. And, as with the launch of any Moschino collab, the internet has gone nuts.\r\n\r\nNow the initial hype is starting to die down, we decided to take a closer look at the new offering, which has already landed online.\r\n\r\nThe 30-piece collection spans apparel and accessories. The former features a range of tanks, tees and dresses, plus velour tracksuit pieces to make your wildest naughties dreams come true.\r\n\r\nOn the accessories side of things, there\'s MLP backpacks, clutch purses, handbags and phone cases.\r\n\r\nFeast your eyes on the pastel rainbow above.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.moschino.com/au\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">moschino.com/au</a>','A closer look at Moschino\'s My Little Pony capsule collection','','publish','open','open','','a-closer-look-at-moschinos-my-little-pony-capsule-collection','','','2017-09-26 02:45:28','2017-09-26 02:45:28','',0,'http://localhost/?p=1000',0,'post','',0),(1001,4,'2017-09-26 02:40:47','2017-09-26 02:40:47','','Moschino_My_Little_Pony_collection_1','','inherit','open','closed','','moschino_my_little_pony_collection_1','','','2017-09-26 02:40:47','2017-09-26 02:40:47','',1000,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Moschino_My_Little_Pony_collection_1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1002,4,'2017-09-26 02:40:49','2017-09-26 02:40:49','','Moschino_My_Little_Pony_collection_2','','inherit','open','closed','','moschino_my_little_pony_collection_2','','','2017-09-26 02:40:49','2017-09-26 02:40:49','',1000,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Moschino_My_Little_Pony_collection_2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1003,4,'2017-09-26 02:40:50','2017-