ve for Glossier, the cult beauty label has announced it’s releasing a candle. But, that’s not the most exciting part.\r\n\r\nGlossier will rely on its loyal fan base to suggest fragrance ideas for the new candle, which means you might just have your dream scent realised.\r\n\r\nThe idea is still in the very early stages, with the brand’s product developer asking customers for their opinions via its blog.\r\n\r\nIt’s not the first time Glossier has relied on its fan base for direction. It’s also been used to determine which countries the brand <a href=\"http://intothegloss.com/2017/07/where-can-i-buy-glossier-canada-uk-france/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">should head to next</a>.\r\n\r\nThis time around, Glossier is asking for customers\' dream scents, referencing the popularity of cult candle Diptyque in homes all over the world.\r\n\r\nThe team aren’t after the technical stuff either, no need to include top, middle and base notes. Rather, the brand is looking to build a scent from abstract descriptions of fan\'s favourite scents.\r\n\r\nYou can join in on the conversation right now, by submitting a comment <a href=\"https://intothegloss.com/2017/08/glossier-candle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.\r\n\r\nWho knows, maybe your artistic vision will be realised by Glossier to ignite candles all over the world.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.glossier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">glossier.com</a>','Glossier is releasing a candle and you can suggest the fragrance','','publish','open','open','','glossier-is-releasing-a-candle-and-you-can-suggest-the-fragrance','','','2017-09-26 03:51:44','2017-09-26 03:51:44','',0,'http://localhost/?p=1120',0,'post','',0),(1121,4,'2017-09-26 03:51:31','2017-09-26 03:51:31','','Glossier4_0','','inherit','open','closed','','glossier4_0','','','2017-09-26 03:51:31','2017-09-26 03:51:31','',1120,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Glossier4_0.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1122,4,'2017-09-26 03:51:44','2017-09-26 03:51:44','In a pretty natural move for Glossier, the cult beauty label has announced it’s releasing a candle. But, that’s not the most exciting part.\r\n\r\nGlossier will rely on its loyal fan base to suggest fragrance ideas for the new candle, which means you might just have your dream scent realised.\r\n\r\nThe idea is still in the very early stages, with the brand’s product developer asking customers for their opinions via its blog.\r\n\r\nIt’s not the first time Glossier has relied on its fan base for direction. It’s also been used to determine which countries the brand <a href=\"http://intothegloss.com/2017/07/where-can-i-buy-glossier-canada-uk-france/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">should head to next</a>.\r\n\r\nThis time around, Glossier is asking for customers\' dream scents, referencing the popularity of cult candle Diptyque in homes all over the world.\r\n\r\nThe team aren’t after the technical stuff either, no need to include top, middle and base notes. Rather, the brand is looking to build a scent from abstract descriptions of fan\'s favourite scents.\r\n\r\nYou can join in on the conversation right now, by submitting a comment <a href=\"https://intothegloss.com/2017/08/glossier-candle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.\r\n\r\nWho knows, maybe your artistic vision will be realised by Glossier to ignite candles all over the world.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.glossier.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">glossier.com</a>','Glossier is releasing a candle and you can suggest the fragrance','','inherit','closed','closed','','1120-revision-v1','','','2017-09-26 03:51:44','2017-09-26 03:51:44','',1120,'http://localhost/uncategorized/1120-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1123,4,'2017-09-26 04:00:32','2017-09-26 04:00:32','<strong>Name: </strong>Black Leopard Nourishing Lip Balm For Men\r\n<strong>Price: </strong>$9.95\r\n<strong>What it does:</strong> A lip balm for men which hydrates the lips to relieve dryness with a \'triple action formula\'\r\n<strong>Key ingredients:</strong> seed oil, Crea Alba, lanolin, cacao seed butter, peppermint oil, Bergamot fruit oil ++ more\r\n<strong>Available from:</strong> <a href=\"http://blackleopardskincare.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blackleopardskincare.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>How it feels/smells/looks</strong>\r\n\r\nThis lip balm has a smooth and silky feeling upon application. If your lips are dry, they definitely won’t stay that way after application.\r\n\r\n<strong>Why I like it</strong>\r\n\r\nThe peppermint aftertaste makes you want to re-apply just for the taste. Your lips feel smooth and moist.\r\n\r\n<strong>Areas for improvement</strong>\r\n\r\nThe glossy residue the product leaves on your lips makes them sparkle. This may not appeal to every man, however, I personally like looking glossy.\r\n\r\n<strong>Final comments</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you’re not afraid to enhance your pout and you like a peppermint aftertaste, then this balm is for you. It doesn\'t really differ to lip balm that\'s targeted at women but it\'s great there are products that are specifically targeted at men.\r\n\r\nThe packaging also has a picture of a tiger which makes it more masculine, and therefore more acceptable for boys to use.','Beauty report: Black Leopard Nourishing Lip Balm For Men','','publish','open','open','','beauty-report-black-leopard-nourishing-lip-balm-for-men','','','2017-09-26 04:00:32','2017-09-26 04:00:32','',0,'http://localhost/?p=1123',0,'post','',0),(1124,4,'2017-09-26 04:00:21','2017-09-26 04:00:21','','Leopard nourishing balm_0','','inherit','open','closed','','leopard-nourishing-balm_0','','','2017-09-26 04:00:21','2017-09-26 04:00:21','',1123,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Leopard-nourishing-balm_0.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1125,4,'2017-09-26 04:00:32','2017-09-26 04:00:32','<strong>Name: </strong>Black Leopard Nourishing Lip Balm For Men\r\n<strong>Price: </strong>$9.95\r\n<strong>What it does