=We%20Recommend%20Carousel_5&amp;featureref1=we%20recommend\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">asos.com/au</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>How it feels/smells/looks</strong>\r\n\r\nDefinitely feels like silicone on the fingers but goes on matte and feels quite hydrating. As for the packaging, it’s a blogger\'s dream: silver, black and white.\r\n\r\n<strong>Why I like it</strong>\r\n\r\nThe price!!! It’s a drug store price for a high-end primer. It also doesn’t leave that waxy, mask feeling that lots of matte primers do. I’ve tried many expensive variations and this primer is up there with the best.\r\n\r\n<strong>Areas for improvement</strong>\r\n\r\nDefinitely requires drying time before adding foundation, but for $9 I have all the time in the world.\r\n\r\n<strong>Final comments</strong>\r\n\r\nBecause it has a matte finish, those with dry skin might prefer the brand\'s other primers. Also, less is definitely more with this baby, I found my foundation peeling if I applied too much.','Beauty report: The Ordinary High Adherence Silicone Primer','','publish','open','open','','beauty-report-the-ordinary-high-adherence-silicone-primer','','','2017-09-26 07:51:41','2017-09-26 07:51:41','',0,'http://localhost/?p=1142',0,'post','',0),(1143,4,'2017-09-26 07:44:33','2017-09-26 07:44:33','','Laneway_Magical_Cloudz-3_0','','inherit','open','closed','','laneway_magical_cloudz-3_0','','','2017-09-26 07:44:45','2017-09-26 07:44:45','',1135,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Laneway_Magical_Cloudz-3_0.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1144,4,'2017-09-26 07:44:37','2017-09-26 07:44:37','','Danny-Barwick1_0','','inherit','open','closed','','danny-barwick1_0','','','2017-09-26 07:45:16','2017-09-26 07:45:16','',1135,'http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Danny-Barwick1_0.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1146,4,'2017-09-26 07:51:20','2017-09-26 07:51:20','','TheOrdinaryPrimer_0','','inherit','open','closed','','theordinaryprimer_0','','','2017-09-26 07:51:20','2017-09-26 